                  </hi>. This appears to be part of the iron the barge was loaded with—I have weighed the iron in the barge, and there is 18 cwt. short.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Chambers</hi>. I was coming through the Borough market by Southwark bridge, and met Ragan coming along with the iron.</p>
